{
  "stem": "23742.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And lots of people wanted to hear about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as time went by, I I felt more rational, that I could talk about it and-- and in more detail.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I must confess, I lost part of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Although, my family was orthodox, as the years progressed, I felt that I was more secular than orthodox.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all kinds of questions were being made by Anglo-jury as to why it happened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where was God?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And things like that-- and I had very mixed feelings as to how, why, what, and when.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But without wishing to offend those of the more orthodox kind, I have to admit that my faith in God had diminished somewhat.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Perhaps, my views were unfounded, but that's the way I felt at the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and from then on, once I became more secular in my attitude, I'm still a Jew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I recognize that I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I observe the customs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I go to shul on various occasions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And that's as far as it went.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had no reason to regret my previous life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was still a relatively young man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And my thoughts at that time was I have a wife.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my son was born the 1st of May 1946.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to provide a living for them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was my aim, to make up for the five and a half years that I had spent during the war and to make a home, achieve something for myself.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as the years went by, I did that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the first trade, of course, was the one that I left in '39, which was back to tailoring.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that wasn't for me.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
